			<div class="menu-tns-nav-2018-primary-topics-container"><ul id="menu-tns-nav-2018-primary-topics" class="menu"><li id="menu-item-5771442" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-home menu-item-has-children menu-item-5771442"><a href="https://thenewstack.io/">Architecture</a>
