	>

	<H3>A newsletter digest of the weeks most important stories & analyses.</H3>

	<div class="newsletter-sign-up-form">

		<input class="newsletter-sign-up-input" type="email" placeholder="Email Address">

		<div class="newsletter-sign-up-subscriptions">

			<div class="ebooks-2017-settings-header">
				Do you also want to be notified of the following?
			</div>

			<div>
				<label class="no-select">
					<input
						id="nl-subs-all"
						type="checkbox"
