	<header class="title-row">

		<h4>
	        <a href="https://thenewstack.io/category/tools/" alt="View all posts in Tools">Tools</a>	    </h4>

		<h2 class="small">
			<a href="https://thenewstack.io/chef-opens-its-code-base-says-goodbye-to-open-core/">Chef Opens Its Code Base, Says Goodbye to Open Core</a>
		</h2>

		<h4 class="timestamp">2 Apr 2019 10:03am,

